LOAD LINK 2: <a href=\"http://dler.org/dl.php?id=210\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdler.org%2Fdl.php%3Fid%3D210&d=RL%2F4GsenS2qWDYAFVAcYZ2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=456e6fc7\" target=\"_blank\">http://dler.org/dl.php?id=210</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果之前有玩過新幹線版 ! 可以睇呢條片知道G級有咩分別 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kA9klDVr_uE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkA9klDVr_uE&d=RL%2F4GsenS2qWDYAFVAcYZ2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=ad15f7ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kA9klDVr_uE</a> <br />\n<br />\n如果你只玩過掌機芒亨，可以睇呢條片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q-8vJm4Bz4c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dq-8vJm4Bz4c&d=RL%2F4GsenS2qWDYAFVAcYZ2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=78b2684e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q-8vJm4Bz4c</a> <br />\n<br />\n如果你玩都未玩過，更加要睇上面2條片, 雖然日文, 但有個概念知道玩乜 <br />\n以下係HD畫質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rQs7GVzFqDI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrQs7GVzFqDI&d=RL%2F4GsenS2qWDYAFVAcYZ2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=19766a1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rQs7GVzFqDI</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s24.postimg.org/h4vg4dntx/000000.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs24.postimg.org%2Fh4vg4dntx%2F000000.png&h=4086b59a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s24.postimg.org/yjfocnkyt/XFpicture23106.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs24.postimg.org%2Fyjfocnkyt%2FXFpicture23106.jpg&h=96f853af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n獵團一週年拍照 <br />\n<br />\n有意加入高登獵團者請聯絡團長 ~ <br />\n<br />\n高登獵團參 <br />\n團長︰你老味比比比 ID: 49UDVU <br />\n另主要用line交流, line id: hkg_mhf <br />\n<br />\n台灣小部屋(wiki): <a href=\"http://myleoworld.myds.me/home/mhfg/\" data-sr-ur