k\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1vNLpPcZerv_SH_hWRu-Pywd8CEbrDEOilXE5MMS-YPQ/edit?usp=sharing</a> <br />\n[/url]<br />\n懶唔想用砌裝器都得 你直接講你想要既技 <br />\n我幫你搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0994094e3329db7e465811fb90dc49ec9b7c9c66","tid":42413,"uid":63371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T16:26:58.000Z","msg":"Q&amp;A(詳細版<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/14mM29NsdbH8LnleOr8TDwrBKtrUXVsDD0LKHc1G-eXU/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F14mM29NsdbH8LnleOr8TDwrBKtrUXVsDD0LKHc1G-eXU%2Fedit&d=RL%2F4GsenS2qWDYAFVAcYZ2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=a616552a\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/14mM29NsdbH8LnleOr8TDwrBKtrUXVsDD0LKHc1G-eXU/edit</a>) <br />\n<br />\nQ1. 新GAME黎?? <br />\nA1. G版係, 但MHF出左3年幾, 之前新斷線經營不善執左 <br />\n而家由台灣CAPCOM自己直營<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 追緊日版進度, 暫時只有一年差距 <br />\n<br />\nQ2. PSV係咪得日服PSN先玩到?? <br />\nA2. 亞服黎, 要開多個PSN, 即係同PS3一樣 <br />\n<br />\nQ4. PC用月費計定咩?? 好似好多收費方案 <br />\nA4. <br />\n月費, PC: my card 300點, PSN 300魔物幣 <br />\n<br />\n另外有100點VIP, 300 恩典同400 恩典增幅 一日, <br />\n對比起日版, 亞服可以講話超值 <br />\n因為亞服100點1日全包宴, 日服則分類仔細d <br />\n<br />\n參考用, 邊到買到平mycard (非打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\nhtmgame <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.htmgame.com/card/42.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.htmgame.com%2Fcard%2F42.html&d=RL%2F4GsenS2qWDYAFVAcYZ2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=9d21feb0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.htmgame.com/card/42.html</a> <br />\n288 <br />\n<a href=\"http://288game.com/index.php?r=product%2Findex&amp;id=12\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F288game.com%2Findex.php%3Fr%3Dproduct%252Findex%26id%3D12&d=RL%2F4GsenS2qWDYAFVAcYZ2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=80d435f7\" target=\"_blank\">http://288game.com/index.php?r=product%2Findex&amp;id=12</a> <br />\n520game <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.520game.com.hk/shop/?product-3253.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.520game.com.hk%2Fshop%2F%3Fproduct-3253.html&d=RL%2F4GsenS2qWDYAFVAcYZ2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=779ec365\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.520game.com.hk/shop/?product-3253.html</a> <br />\n<br />\nQ5. PS3 點樣買方案？ <br />\nA5. 【PS3 商城道具購買方式及說明】 <br />\nQ: 商城使用的〔魔物幣〕要如何購買兌換？ <br />\n1.欲購入商城商品，必須先於PS Store購入魔物幣(需先儲值PSN點數） <br />\n2.後續於遊戲登入介面之〔遊戲商城〕中選擇欲購買之商品 <br />\n註：PSV買完魔物幣要15分鐘先會過數落capcom户口內，如果在遊戲內，必須要登出遊戲及重新啟動遊戲才會啟動幣值，如没有重新啟動情況下，需要等待下回啟動方可生效幣值，我第一次買魔物幣等左4個鐘都冇，係因為係遊戲內冇登出過，結果問capcom先知道�� <br />\n<br />\nG6有HD版 電腦需求：<a href=\"http://members.mhf-g.jp/contents/hg/spec.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmembers.mhf-g.jp%2Fcontents%2Fhg%2Fspec.html&d=RL%2F4GsenS2qWDYAFVAcYZ2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=eeb238a4\" target=\"_blank\">http://members.mhf-g.jp/contents/hg/spec.html</a> <br />\n用<span style=\"color: red;\">IE</span>直接check <br />\n<a href=\"http://members.mh-frontier.jp/contents_sys/analyze2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmembers.mh-frontier.jp%2Fcontents_sys%2Fanalyze2%2F&d=RL%2F4GsenS2qWDYAFVAcYZ2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=594ec904\" target=\"_blank\">http://members.mh-frontier.jp/contents_sys/analyze2/</a> <br />\n<br />\n詳細資料(整理中...) 睇住先, 應該解答到新玩既朋友大部分問題 <br />\n有咩唔明係個POST問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n宜家4大活動冇間斷輪流開, G10會暫停天廊<br />\n極征 <br />\n大航祭 <br />\n獵人祭 <br />\n天廊 <br />\n所以暫時唔洗擔心miss左, 一路未改G10, 一個月後又有得打 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新玩同回流既巴打有福啦 <br />\n修練/回歸區開放<br />\n<br />\n追上進度 冇難度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://mhfg.capcom.com.tw/comeback/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmhfg.capcom.com.tw%2Fcomeback%2F&d=RL%2F4GsenS2qWDYAFVAcYZ2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=609b8631\" target=\"_blank\">http://mhfg.capcom.com.tw/comeback/</a> <br />\n呢隻game上到G位先係真正既開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nd圖死左 我又懶得整新圖 所以純文字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n由0開始極速上G位教學 <span style=\"color: red;\">(修練/回歸區專用)</span> <br />\n必須條件：每個月既15號或之前開始玩 <br />\n因為要拎一個月內登入15日既獎勵 <br />\n所以你月中先開始玩 我會建議你等下先 一係你直接課金 開vip <br />\n例子 4月1-15日開ac玩（4月有30日） <br />\n5月1-16日開ac玩 (5月有31日) <br />\n<br />\n開完角色之後就做新手任 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後你有14天時間自由玩下 了解下要做乜 <br />\n可以做下活動任 / 武器 / 防具 / 裝飾品 <br />\n<br />\n同開賴狩人 要去打隻怪鳥 <br />\n<br />\n開同伴 (HR11以上 &amp; 改築上手・匠の技 ) <br />\n最好升到hr51以上 到第15日先升到hr100 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">hr1-99 係唔洗比月費 所以可以之後先比錢</span> <br />\n<br />\n第15日開始 拎到一日VIP <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想再快d就課400恩典<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n去官網個虛寶郵箱度拎 <br />\n去酒吧開傳奇獵人(npc) 自己簡個鐘意既用 我多數用蕾拉/芙蘿拉 <br />\n最好幫個npc 熄哂全部道具 <br />\n開始衝G位 <br />\n去回歸區 <br />\n有個任叫 HRP大量獲得！ XXX <br />\n完任果陣係領取報酬素材果度 拎張 公會特別推薦信 放係身 <br />\n其他素材 可以直接出售 / 送至道具箱 <br />\n升到hr100就去搵公會會長 <br />\n簡 HR試煉內容2 其他可以唔洗理 <br />\n冇錢? 就去打錢 有任係專門打 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n升到hr500 開始有sr <br />\n去裝備箱 裝 秘傳書 <br />\n右面個表 一項係HC適正xxxx稀有度：5 <br />\n只要用 5或以下既武器 打HC任就會多d經 <br />\n所以 呢度開始用番你最廢果把武器就得 唔洗煩 <br />\n係模式到轉 HC任會有個&quot;火&quot; icon<br />\n我建議將全部武器既sr升到999 <br />\n一把武器大約一個鐘度 <br />\n<br />\n經過一段時間後 <br />\n<br />\n升G位果個任 搵我地幫手打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後做獵人導引既任 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最基本既G位入門裝 (入門GF + 蠻龍劍珠GF)"},{"pid":"dd2f79b17c6642d7d223b236578f831f637c2bc5","tid":42413,"uid":12356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T17:12:04.000Z","msg":"新手留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74d98b38b4a00312c47f0db45a3a761f28fb9ba8","tid":42413,"uid":12356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T02:43:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"249cee371dcba8765a58cd76ef033e3364c2937d","tid":42413,"uid":37374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T03:59:00.000Z","msg":"sr999 係咪好似先前果d咩嵐弓？果時係要買6倍經刷好耐先升爆？依加一個鐘升爆咁正？"},{"pid":"4f9e74219cb9ca97e22730968042005bed9d194a","tid":42413,"uid":12356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T04:11:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>sr999 係咪好似先前果d咩嵐弓？果時係要買6倍經刷好耐先升爆？依加一個鐘升爆咁正？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"773f02e8b56b4c57cf16848ab69ee7c8658e3781","tid":42413,"uid":37374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T10:59:07.000Z","msg":"想問下一個人打，d野會唔會少血d？慣左玩psp單機先有feel(同識既fd玩例外)"},{"pid":"0360f8db4ebd21e855e888fbe8f0a38a8c952647","tid":42413,"uid":37374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T13:00:12.000Z","msg":"想玩HD版係咪只可以玩日服?"},{"pid":"274670fc80ce864d0548c5728fb05bf59647cd2a","tid":42413,"uid":12356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T16:27:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下一個人打，d野會唔會少血d？慣左玩psp單機先有feel(同識既fd玩例外)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔會"},{"pid":"2f9184cdc09b95f0704eeab2075d2d627b682d72","tid":42413,"uid":12356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T16:28:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想玩HD版係咪只可以玩日服?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n宜家得pc有高清<br />\n/<br />\n將來更新到mhfz 既ps4有高清<br />\n<br />\n宜家係mhfg9 -&gt;mhfg10-&gt;mhfz"},{"pid":"6f5b8593c4d78c4be2c0e8c81e5ba52fbc4fb992","tid":42413,"uid":37374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T16:31:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想玩HD版係咪只可以玩日服?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n宜家得pc有高清<br />\n/<br />\n將來更新到mhfz 既ps4有高清<br />\n<br />\n宜家係mhfg9 -&gt;mhfg10-&gt;mhfz</blockquote><br />\n姐係第一條LINK個台服已經係HD版?"},{"pid":"324c0d641472fc0ce4fe89b1dac7a67946f96e32","tid":42413,"uid":12356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T16:58:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想玩HD版係咪只可以玩日服?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n宜家得pc有高清<br />\n/<br />\n將來更新到mhfz 既ps4有高清<br />\n<br />\n宜家係mhfg9 -&amp;gt;mhfg10-&amp;gt;mhfz</blockquote><br />\n姐係第一條LINK個台服已經係HD版?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n登入前<br />\n係下面個環境設定度開"},{"pid":"1e7b8b96589f8d305293f87df5b96602fbe2d4b4","tid":42413,"uid":12356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T01:13:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e6a2535c005c9a34603970e5e36a8e86cc73f9f","tid":42413,"uid":37374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T02:07:15.000Z","msg":"啱啱裝完，發覺d制好似唔match既(手制)跑步都跑唔到"},{"pid":"b8ec31918f7975422dbecccf5f6d14ca5f2f2caf","tid":42413,"uid":3332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T02:14:14.000Z","msg":"好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf47e7e3c2a05302c6fd31c91f031d7bdf20faec","tid":42413,"uid":12356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T05:07:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱啱裝完，發覺d制好似唔match既(手制)跑步都跑唔到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要去改制<br />\n<br />\n如果你用xboxone手制就安心上路<br />\nLT 同 RT 會用唔到<br />\n上網有方法解決 但我唔識<br />\n<br />\n360 ps4 ps3 完全冇間題"},{"pid":"24d42912e81a17ad582c1eccf3d76f32c388f9fb","tid":42413,"uid":12356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T05:08:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都係一日3蚊姐 <br />\n你咪當日日買旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9bf2f4c077b6f8040155c10318755d263105d74","tid":42413,"uid":63371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T14:13:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啱啱裝完，發覺d制好似唔match既(手制)跑步都跑唔到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要去改制<br />\n<br />\n如果你用xboxone手制就安心上路<br />\nLT 同 RT 會用唔到<br />\n上網有方法解決 但我唔識<br />\n<br />\n360 ps4 ps3 完全冇間題</blockquote><br />\n因為玩MHP, 所以以前新幹線都沿用C字手, 中段有FD話可以改用磨菇轉視點已經放棄用C字手, 手指冇咁攰。今時g版手制設定如果set &quot;掌機模式&quot;已經可以直接用磨菇轉, 唔洗入開記事本setting改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b97d2cf5adda9f503c9f87b1f7d6df5e1e3358f3","tid":42413,"uid":37374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T16:05:31.000Z","msg":"得30FPS玩到頭暈,有冇方法開60FPS?"},{"pid":"af153f69cd99902a5d9d038198a82d7447c44c51","tid":42413,"uid":63371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T04:10:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得30FPS玩到頭暈,有冇方法開60FPS?</blockquote><br />\n開左高清?? game本身冇FPS調較, 試下唔開睇下會唔會好d?<br />\n另外你有冇玩過手提版MH? 一樣會暈?"},{"pid":"095378b2087491e3f540ae2344579d15f8c00891","tid":42413,"uid":12356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T14:30:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ed62176b5b09952f7f512e2e10b7c39aa18919b","tid":42413,"uid":12356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T03:41:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e0f81fcee89da0f4b314c00678b91e1ceab0925","tid":42413,"uid":12356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T22:46:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e426c3cb19ac238db01fbdeab69f63d2b5b8ff","tid":42413,"uid":63371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T13:26:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03357b36e282154dd05a967ed90339489daf1a0d","tid":42413,"uid":12356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02: